---
title: Creamy Mushroom Casserole with Veggie Mash & Lemony Baby Broccoli
description: Savour the richness of this creamy casserole, where mushrooms are the start of the show! Carrot adds a new layer of flavour to
your much-loved potato mash, and forms the perfect base to soak up this creamy, hearty delight.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
